Organization : 
- create work shift model (regular, 2 Shift, 24 hours Shift) along with start and end working hours
- Salary Range Setting per Position
- Organization structure workflow for approval

Notification: 
- Notification for approval/rejection on leave, overtime, etc
- Notification using push notification and email

Settings:
- Grade definition and salary range


Create plan to extend detail departments to enable work model (regular, shift)
1. assign department work model from work model created. one department can have multi work model
2. assign employees to selected model (can be all employee or selected), one employee only can be assign to one work model.
3. create function to generate work schedule (regular, weekend not included) / roster (for shift, minimum employee) for each employee selected in this active month. 
4. the work schedule will be compared to the actual clock-in/out in attendance then the process will produce timesheet for each employee.
5. The timesheet will be used as reference for payroll
don't be shy to ask for clarification if you need to.